by javiereguiluz at 2019-02-04T17:01:10Z

To give some more context, `guid` database types comes from:

* https://github.com/doctrine/dbal/blob/92920ede68e1d16246712cd41318dd82bb72c015/lib/Doctrine/DBAL/Types/Type.php#L42
* https://github.com/doctrine/dbal/blob/master/lib/Doctrine/DBAL/Types/GuidType.php

But let's merge this to fix the other occurrences. Thanks Olivier!
